{{flavour|Recalls woodland creatures from elsewhere on the same level.}}

'''Druid's Call''' is monsters-only spell that teleports a random band of natural, animal-intelligence creatures to the caster. Unlike [[Word of Recall]], this spell takes effect instantly.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
This spell was added in [[0.13]].

